</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:00
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='709000' id='t-709000'>I'll show you just one part of our study.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='711000' id='t-711000'>And here I've taken away the robots,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='713000' id='t-713000'>but basically people move with their right arm sinusoidally back and forward.</span>
