12:55
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='764000' id='t-764000'>Now I have to admit, these are the worst studies my lab has ever run.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='767000' id='t-767000'>Because the tickle sensation on the palm comes and goes,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='769000' id='t-769000'>you need large numbers of subjects</span>
