<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='789000' id='t-789000'>And children tend to get into fights which escalate in terms of force.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='792000' id='t-792000'>Now when I screamed at my children to stop,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='794000' id='t-794000'>sometimes they would both say to me</span>
