<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:30
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='799000' id='t-799000'>Now I happen to know my children don't lie,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='801000' id='t-801000'>so I thought, as a neuroscientist,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='803000' id='t-803000'>it was important how I could explain</span>
