<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:59
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='828000' id='t-828000'>So we decided to test this in the lab.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='830000' id='t-830000'>(Laughter)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='833000' id='t-833000'>Now we don't work with children, we don't work with hitting,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='835000' id='t-835000'>but the concept is identical.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='837000' id='t-837000'>We bring in two adults. We tell them they're going to play a game.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='840000' id='t-840000'>And so here's player one and player two sitting opposite to each other.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='842000' id='t-842000'>And the game is very simple.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='844000' id='t-844000'>We started with a motor</span>
