<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1007000' id='t-1007000'>So what is it about a movement which is good or bad?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1009000' id='t-1009000'>Imagine I want to intercept this ball.</span>
